  [Text] Sarajevo, 17 Apr (TANJUG) -- Srpska republic 
president Radovan Karadzic said in Pale this evening that an 
agreement has been reached on an immediate cease-fire, "certain 
separation of the forces," and a maximum of restraint from 
military operations in the Gorazde area. 
  After his talks with Yasushi Akashi, the UN secretary 
general's special envoy, Karadzic said that if the cease-fire is 
