<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Events in Sarajevo -- 17 April </PHRASE></F></HT>
<H4>    Capture Serb-Held Villages </H4>

<F P=102> LD1704180694 Sarajevo Radio Bosnia-Herzegovina Network in 
Serbo-Croatian 1700 GMT 17 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD1704180694 </F>
<F P=104>  Sarajevo Radio Bosnia-Herzegovina Network </F>
