<H3> <TI>   Serbs Threaten Retaliation Against Croatia </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Serbs Threaten Retaliation Against Croatia </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD1704152094 Belgrade TANJUG Domestic Service in 
