<H3> <TI>   Mihai Denies IZVESTIYA Interview </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Mihai Denies IZVESTIYA Interview </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   AU1904085794 Bucharest EVENIMENTUL ZILEI in Romanian 14 Apr 
94 p 8 </F>

<F P=103> AU1904085794 </F>
<F P=104>  Bucharest EVENIMENTUL ZILEI </F>
<F P=105>  Romanian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [Communique issued by ex-King Mihai's Press Bureau in </F>
Versoix on 13 April 1994: "King Mihai Has Never Granted an 
Interview to IZVESTIYA"] 
  [Text] The Press Bureau of His Majesty King Mihai is 
empowered to issue the following communique: 
  In accordance with the news published by EVENIMENTUL ZILEI 
on 
13 April, we note that His Majesty King Mihai has never held a 
dialogue with any representative of the Russian daily IZVESTIYA 
on the issue of the current fate of Romania, the future of the 
royal family, or on any other issue. 
  Note of the editorial office: 
  Indeed, King Mihai I has not granted an interview to 
IZVESTIYA. It was a reproduction of an interview granted by His 
Majesty to the Swiss daily "24 HOURS." 
  The way in which IZVESTYIA presented this interview has 
caused some confusion. 

</TEXT>

