  [Text] Sarajevo, 14 Apr (TANJUG) -- The supreme command of 
the Srpska republic armed forces this evening issued a statement 
calling on citizens of Muslim and Serb nationalities from the 
Gorazde area to take refuge behind the Serb lines, where they 
will be guaranteed security and protection. 
  Full security and protection is also guaranteed to all 
members of military and police units who end attacks on Serb 
