  [Excerpts] [Announcer Paul Amar] Let's return to the 
deterioration of the situation in Gorazde in Bosnia, because we 
now have live with us from Geneva Mrs Berthiaume. Good evening. 
You are the spokesperson of the UNHCR in Geneva, so you have 
information from Gorazde that we may not have. Can you tell me 
this information about what is happening in that town, that has 
been surrounded by the Serbs. 
