<H3> <TI>   `Albanisation' Reported in Tetovo </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    `Albanisation' Reported in Tetovo </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   AU1904202494 Skopje MILS-NEWS in English 19 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> AU1904202494 </F>
<F P=104>  Skopje MILS-NEWS </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [Unattributed report: "Albanisation of Tetovo"] </F>
  [Text] The Macedonian [The Former Yugoslav Republic of 
Macedonia -- FYROM] Radio informs of recently increasing 
practice of Macedonians selling their homes in Tetovo. 
Purchasers are mainly Albanians from outside, offering 
enormously high prices in hard currency. The tax department in 
Tetovo has received 1,700 applications for house, business 
locals and real estates sales, only in the period from last 
January until this month. The sales are especially frequent in 
the city centre. The basic reasons for this is the present 
chaotic and lawless situation, expelling the official Macedonian 
language from use and the uncontrolled processes of Albanisation 
of Tetovo and surrounding villages. 

</TEXT>

